#etcsl: line-id=A.9

A.10. umun₂ ak-ak eš₃ e₂-kiš-nu-ŋal₂-la₂-ke₄ mu mah-bi gal-la
#lem: umun[knowledge]; ak[do]; eš[shrine]; Ekišnuŋal[1]TN; mu[name]; mah[great]; gal[big]
#etcsl: line-id=A.10

