#lem: šag[heart]; inimŋal[eloquent]; kisikil[young woman]; Ningal[1]DN; unu[dwelling]; gal[big]; til[live (of a single person)]
#etcsl: line-id=A.11

A.12. muš₃-me sag₉ nitalam₂ ki aŋ₂ {d}nun-bar-še-gu-nu
