#etcsl: line-id=A.12

A.13. lu₂ mu mah mussa kur gal a-a {d}en-lil₂-la₂-kam
#lem: lu[person]; mu[name]; mah[great]; mussa[son-in-law]; kur[mountain(s)]; gal[big]; aya[father]; Enlil[1]DN
#etcsl: line-id=A.13

A.14. saŋŋa ban₃-da igi-ŋal₂-tuku pad₃-da an ki-bi-da-ke₄
#lem: saŋŋa[an official]; banda[junior]; igiŋaltuku[wise]; pad[find]; an[sky]; ki[place]
#etcsl: line-id=A.14

A.15. gu₂-un diŋir-re-[e-ne] šu gid₂-i ma-dam kur ab su₃-ud-da inim-ma-ni bur₂-e
